## Research Patterns

### Competitive Analysis

```
firecrawl_agent({
  prompt: "How do [Company A], [Company B], and [Company C] implement [feature]? Compare their approaches, focusing on [specific aspects].",
  schema: {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "competitors": {
        "type": "array",
        "items": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "name": { "type": "string" },
            "approach": { "type": "string" },
            "strengths": { "type": "string" },
            "weaknesses": { "type": "string" }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
})
```

### Implementation Patterns

```
firecrawl_agent({
  prompt: "Find production examples of [technology] being used for [use case]. Include code patterns, common gotchas, and performance considerations."
})
```

### Architecture Research

```
firecrawl_agent({
  prompt: "What architectures do major platforms use for [requirement]? Focus on scalability, maintainability, and real-world trade-offs."
})
```

